works.description:
Back in February, we saw for the first  
time the Fiat 500 by Gucci, an upshot of a collaboration between Gucci’s  
creative director Frida Giannini and Fiat’s Centro Stile. The Fiat 500 by  
Gucci has now made its Parisian debut. Gucci Creative Director Frida  
Giannini was on hand to present the special edition of the iconic Fiat 500.
